  <Zomboss.label>僵王博士</Zomboss.label>
  <!-- EN: A mad scientist obsessed with zombie research. He'll test your defenses with frequent and varied events.\n\nHis experiments sometimes involve other factions, but his beloved zombies are never far away. -->
